query:
SELECT r.id as routeId, r.userId, r.name, w.contactName, w.rescheduledDate
FROM routes r
INNER JOIN route_waypoints w ON r.id = w.routeId
WHERE w.rescheduledDate IS NOT NULL
LIMIT 5;
